cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper is about image restoration, which is a topic in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a method for training the parameters of the model, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-categories of machine learning, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of nonlinear reaction diffusion models and linear filters suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of neural networks, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions the use of GPUs for parallel computation, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of multimedia, cs.MM (Multimedia).
